snippet.textDisplay:
"Fassle" isn’t just about love it’s about life, change, and the quiet distances that grow between people, places, and even parts of ourselves.
Kavish beautifully puts into words that strange feeling when everything looks fine, but something inside feels… off. The song speaks to those moments when you're surrounded by people, yet you feel a little alone.

It’s introspective, poetic, and deeply relatable. Whether it’s friendships, family, or your own thoughts—Fassle is that soft reminder that sometimes, growing up also means growing apart.
